---
title: The Hot Chick Crispy Chicken & Halloumi Burger, Hot Honey, Sesame Wedges and Lime Mayo Slaw
description: This Crispy Chicken & Halloumi Burger, Hot Honey, Sesame Wedges and Lime Mayo Slaw is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
